//This Query will pull a users activity timeline in Azure. It shows interactive and non interactive sign ins as well as other useful information (see line 7).
//This only works if you have Azure AD
AADSignInEventsBeta
//CloudAppEvents
//Comment out line 2 and remove comments from line 3 to see what the user was doing via cloud app events for example: opening email.
| where AccountDisplayName contains ""
| project Timestamp, Application,LogonType, AccountDisplayName, AccountUPN, UserAgent, ClientAppUsed, IPAddress, Country, State, City, AuthenticationRequirement, DeviceName, OSPlatform, DeviceTrustType, AADDeviceID
| sort by Timestamp desc
